item.title: Cant connect to my server wdf
item.dc:creator: @Emchie Emchie
item.description:
@Emchie wrote:

Server Might have a different port. For example, port 9092, and the client might be set to use that port.

Or, Its a Non-Silab server, that will only allow clients with a newer cache to log on to it.
